               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18381231-name-76" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18381231-name-76" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18381231-name-76" type="surname" value="CASTLE"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18381231-name-76" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE CASTLE</persName>
                  </hi>. I live with Mr. Painter, in Broad way, Westminster. I was standing at his door at three o'clock on the afternoon of the 10th of December, at the horse's head, minding the gig—I saw the prisoner snatch my master's cloak out at the side of the gig, roll it up, and give it to another boy—they both ran off—I gave an alarm, the boy dropped it, and it was picked up—the prisoner was taken the same evening—I am quite certain he is the boy.</p>
               <p>
